So, this isn’t exactly 1 charity, but it is a HUGE thing with many animal shelters (specifically dog shelters)

A LOT of shelters aren’t getting enough adoptions (some are getting none at all) due to the COVID-19 panic, so the shelters have started becoming very crowded, so a lot of dogs have gotten euthanized.... If there’s any charities you guys can find and donate to, even if it’s just a small animal shelter or if it’s a big one, that would be so great....

I know I’m not the only person who is worried about these animals’ lives, and I just want to raise some awareness about this because not many people even know that this is happening....

Thank you guys so very much for raising money for the COVID-19 charities, by the way!! You both are so amazing and hilarious, and thank you for providing an outlet for so many people during this quarantine!! 💝💖💝💖💝💖💝💖💝💖💝💖💝💖💝💖💝💖💝💖
